OL,3,CStarmer faces criticism over
OL,4,Cimmigration plans
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister faces criticism
OL,7,Ffrom multiple quarters after unveiling
OL,8,Fhis Government's plan to cut net
OL,9,Fmigration on Monday.
OL,11,FThe plans, which are expected to
OL,12,Freduce the number of people coming to
OL,13,Fthe UK by up to 100,000 per year,
OL,14,Finclude reforming work and study visas
OL,15,Fand requiring a higher level of
OL,16,FEnglish across all immigration routes.
