OL,3,CStarmer faces criticism over
OL,4,Cimmigration plans
OL,6,FBut Monday's proposals sparked concern
OL,7,Ffrom employers, particularly in the
OL,8,Fcare sector, following the
OL,9,Fannouncement that care worker visas
OL,10,Fwould be scrapped.
OL,12,FGMB national officer Will Dalton said
OL,13,Fthe decision would be "potentially
OL,14,Fcatastrophic" as the care sector was
OL,15,F"utterly reliant on migrant workers"
OL,16,Fand still had more than 130,000
OL,17,Fvacancies across the country.
