OL,6,FThe Home Office believes there are
OL,7,F40,000 potential members of staff
OL,8,Foriginally brought over by "rogue"
OL,9,Fproviders who could work in the sector
OL,10,Fwhile UK staff are trained up.
OL,12,FMore broadly, CBI chief executive Rain
OL,13,FNewton-Smith warned that labour
OL,14,Fshortages "can't be solved by training
OL,15,Falone" in the context of a shrinking
OL,16,Fworkforce and an ageing population.
