OL,6,FShe also cautioned that changes that
OL,7,F"risk making the UK a less attractive
OL,8,Fplace to study" or increased costs for
OL,9,Funiversities "will have knock-on
OL,10,Fimpacts for the competitive strength
OL,11,Fof UK higher education".
OL,13,FIn the Commons, Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,14,Fannouncement has also drawn attacks
OL,15,Ffrom across the political spectrum.
