OL,6,FSheffield Hallam MP Olivia Blake
OL,7,Fsuggested the phrase could "risk
OL,8,Flegitimising the same far-right
OL,9,Fviolence we saw in last year's summer
OL,10,Friots", while former shadow chancellor
OL,11,FJohn McDonnell, who lost the Labour
OL,12,Fwhip last year, accused Sir Keir of
OL,13,F"reflecting the language" of Enoch
OL,14,FPowell's infamous "rivers of blood"
OL,15,Fspeech in the 1960s.
OL,17,FSkills minister Baroness Jacqui Smith
OL,18,Frejected the comparison, telling BBC
OL,19,FNewsnight it was "wrong".
