OL,6,FMeanwhile, other parties argued the
OL,7,FPrime Minister's proposals did not go
OL,8,Ffar enough.
OL,10,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp said
OL,11,Fthe Immigration White Paper was "so
OL,12,Fweak that it barely scratches the
OL,13,Fsurface" as he pushed for a "binding
OL,14,Fannual cap on migration" and
OL,15,Fdisapplying the Human Rights Act from
OL,16,Fimmigration law.
