OL,6,FNigel Farage, whose Reform UK has
OL,7,Ffocused heavily on immigration in its
OL,8,Fcampaigns, said the Government "will
OL,9,Fnot do what it takes to control our
OL,10,Fborders".
OL,12,FThe Liberal Democrats offered some
OL,13,Fqualified support, with the party's
OL,14,Fhome affairs spokeswoman Lisa Smart
OL,15,Fsaying it was "right that the
OL,16,FGovernment is taking steps to fix our
OL,17,Fbroken immigration system".
